About Me

My mission is to design dan develop great applications that are useful for all.

Hello! Im Muhammad Aulia Alfani. UI/UX designer from Indonesia, Jawa Barat. Passionate in UI/UX design and Front-end web development with high interests in product design, design thinking, social media, digital marketing, and communication. These interests bring me to be an adaptable, creative, and initiative person who pays attention to detail. Love to learn new things, have a high curiosity, and meet new people from different backgrounds.
